    "plain_content":  "Give back to communities\naround the globe.\n\n100% of your donations go toward\nbackpacks and basic supplies for children in need.\n\nTo these kids, *every penny counts.*\n\ndonate now\n\nWhat is Big Heart Backpacks?\n\nBig Heart Backpacks is a non-profit organization that buys backpacks for children in need and fills them with necessities such as: water, snacks, first aid kits, feminine hygiene products, school supplies, down jackets, lightweight blankets, solar powered light bulbs, and other essentials.\n\nOur team organizes trips to rural areas and villages in need to personall y deliver the backpacks.\n\nAll of this is made possibly by you and your generous donations.\n\nReview frequently asked questions,\nvolunteering info, and supplies lists\n\nLearn More\n\n{{Sender_Name}}\n\n{{Sender_Address}} , {{Sender_City}} , {{Sender_State}} {{Sender_Zip}}\n\nUnsubscribe ( {{{unsubscribe}}} ) - Unsubscribe Preferences ( {{{unsubscribe_preferences}}} )\n\n♥ POWERED BY TWILIO SENDGRID ( https://sendgrid.com/ )",
